{"tid":973210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"怪獸媽媽陪碩士女兒見工　搶住問「太熱有無假放」僱主嬲到掟杯","createTime":"2019-01-08T03:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T04:02:05.000Z","uid":152673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e4a3125b80018fecfdf6c7365f74cb9fb0283a03","tid":973210,"uid":152673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T03:22:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2244798/?r=mcsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2244798%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb&d=Mpe9G33sanmsJpFg%2BCLz0xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=e147537a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2244798/?r=mcsdfb</a><br />\n<br />\n香港有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03aa4e44af0b5f8bf48748047d121c6eb36b4203","tid":973210,"uid":152673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T03:23:27.000Z","msg":"發帖的女網民表示，1月4日有女生來應徵丈夫公司，自己則陪同在旁，豈料對方帶同媽媽見工。女生開頭只問了句「請問有勞健保嗎？」媽媽其後搶着問，更接連問了12個問題，包括「假日都放假嗎？」、「颱風天呢？」、「可是我女兒不會開車，騎機車我怕她中暑」、「我女兒有開過刀，腰椎不是很好，會不會需要久坐久站啊？」等。<br />\n<br />\n面對媽媽的接連提問，丈夫都如實一一應答，媽媽最後問到「一個月是多少錢？」聽到是基本薪資起跳，因為不需要專業技術，那位媽媽竟說「我女兒好歹也是碩士，你居然說基本薪資？」"},{"pid":"e068f8767fed1068bf05e3dceafeff5c5e108dc6","tid":973210,"uid":85116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T03:27:08.000Z","msg":"台灣碩士值唔值錢"},{"pid":"30e21893fdfffa0c5af856fe66e6defb8f752239","tid":973210,"uid":119478,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T03:29:27.000Z","msg":"Facebook share就算鳩數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d5b6d028c4b2132bb41ea4be80e97eb1ae0fce","tid":973210,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T03:30:31.000Z","msg":"台灣好多野雞大學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{